text: True Republican was a semi-weekly pro-Republican newspaper published by Boies & Peck in Sycamore, Illinois beginning in 1861 and continued into the late 20th century. It was also known as the Sycamore True Republican. == References == == External links == * Illinois Digital Newspaper Collections: True Republican (1869-1968) Category:Defunct newspapers published in Illinois Category:Sycamore, Illinois Category:1861 establishments in Illinois
